            "content": [
              {
                "nodeType": "text",
                "value": "Place your hand on a plant such as a tree or bush and give it a command. This could be to grow in a certain direction, move a branch in a certain way in order to cover a path or hide something that is on the ground, or obscure a doorway. All plants within 1 space follow the command. The plants take 4 minutes to follow the order.",
